file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Camel K Object API
  version: 1.0.0
  description: A CRUD API for an object store
paths:
  /:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: string
          description: Object list
      operationId: list
      summary: List the objects
  /{name}:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/octet-stream: {}
          description: The object content
      operationId: get
      summary: Get the content of an object
    put:
      requestBody:
        description: The object content
        content:
          application/octet-stream: {}
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: The object has been created
      operationId: create
      summary: Save an object
    delete:
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Object has been deleted
      operationId: delete
      summary: Delete an object
    parameters:
    - name: name
      description: Name of the object
      schema:
        type: string
      in: path
      required: true
